name: Fisherman's hut
address: Pejukutan, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: fantastic view obviously. had fresh octopus with sambal and it was good. chairs rented here for 25k each. open during “Covid times”. they benefit from being the first place on the left side of the beach do ppl are walking from the designated parking area. can’t beat it.
review 2: Beautiful locale with a great view of the sea combined with refreshing drinks and tasty and hygenic food.
review 3:
Best Warung in Atuh Beach 🏝️🤗 Very good service and nice and cozy place with great atmosphere 😊

When you buy food or drink, you can lay down on the sunbeds and relax 🤗

A family business of nice local people, they are always kind and smiling to us 💗
They sell their daily freshly caught fish 🐟🐠🐡and prepare it to your liking 👩🏻‍🍳..if you eat meat, try it ..🤗

We are vegan 🌱 and fish are our friends, no food...😊😅 so we only know from friends..😊 but we were pleasantly surprised that he knows what veganism is...he has no problem modifying food to become vegan 🌱🤗
💛 Mie goreng and Nasi goreng were very good 🤗💛
Every day they have fresh cold coconut 🥥🌴 and fresh fruit juice as well as other cold drinks 😊 After the trip to Atuh it was really a big advantage (tired from the trip to Diamond - from the trip up and down to Atuh 🧗🏻‍♀️ ... Ugh.. 😅)

If you will be in Atuh, you must try it 💛
review 4: Very beautiful views with amazingly delicious food and friendly staff😉

name: ATUH GARDEN BUNGALOW
address: 6JH8+2QP, Pejukutan, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: Madie, the owner is delightful and entertained us with stories of life in Nusa Peneida. He made so much effort to make is feel comfortable. What an awesome experience. He has camping on request which is essentially sleeping on the old style Balinese platform.
review 2: Me and my husband went to this place for honeymoon and love it. It's like out of the normal world, like going back in time without noise and modernization. Everything is going back to nature and pure. I like to be here when you want to get out from work routine. ❤️❤️❤️
